Combating Alien Smuggling What steps are being taken by governmental
or even private entities world-wide to stop the smuggling of aliens.
To be relevant, a document must describe an effort being made (other
than routine border patrols) in any country of the world to prevent
the illegal penetration of aliens across borders.

